# ignores out folder which SHOULD contain all the class files after compiling your project in cmd
# 1. Compile in cmd (just copy and paste)
# 2. javac -d out *.java (COMPILING)
# 3. java -cp out Driver (RUNNING)
# This will make you an out folder
out/

# ignore local database creds so that we don't have to keep pushing/pulling each other's passwords
db.properties